{Speech 4 Answer 4*}{}{[You pay in 200 coins]}
{Speech 4 Answer 4**}{}{[You pay in 500 coins]}
{Speech 4 Answer 4***}{}{[You pay in 1000 coins]}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{It seems I've left my money at home.}
