{Speech 5 Answer 7}{}{An Enlightened one?}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{Oops. Wrong door.}
{Speech 5 Answer 3}{}{Lets move to the moment when I will be served.}
{Speech 6}{}{As long as negative mental energy affects chemical processes in your brain, your real mental potential is depressed. One worse thing is that depressed persons can communicate this energy to other ones. Only people with extremely strong will can be the exception.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Oops. Wrong door.}
{Speech 6 Answer 3}{}{Lets move to the moment when I will be served.}
{Speech 7}{}{Enlightment comes when all your neurodynes are aligned. Then you become AHS, Aligned Hub Seeker, that is the goal of all children of Hub.}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Neurodynes?}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{AHS?}
{Speech 7 Answer 3}{}{Lets move to the moment when I will be served.}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Oops. Wrong door.}
{Speech 8}{}{Neurodynes are mental centers of our bode. Remains of the spirit of those people who died in the War fills your neurodynes with pollution. Since you're born their psy-energy collides with yours and it keep you in depressed state of mood. Alignement removes the pollution.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Oops. Wrong door.}
{Speech 8 Answer 3}{}{Lets move to the moment when I will be served.}
